&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job: Business Integration Lead&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Profile:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Integration Lead, you will own and manage the end-to-end integration of newly acquired operating companies across Banyan Software&#39;s UK &amp;amp; EU portfolio. Acting as the primary point of contact for acquired businesses during their onboarding journey, you will lead integration activities from deal close through to final sign-off, ensuring alignment across finance, systems, compliance, and operational processes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work closely with portfolio company leadership, regional finance teams, and key stakeholders to standardize reporting, integrate systems, and ensure compliance with Banyan&#39;s operating standards. In addition, you will play a key role in developing and refining integration playbooks, SOPs, and scalable processes that support Banyan&#39;s acquisition-driven growth strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role offers a unique opportunity to build and shape a newly established integration function while gaining exposure to M&amp;amp;A integration, finance transformation, ERP implementation, and cross-border business operations within a fast-growing global software organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and lead end-to-end integration programs from acquisition close through final sign-off, managing multiple concurrent integrations at various stages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Function as the primary point of accountability for integration progress, identifying risks, resolving issues, and escalating critical blockers when required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, maintain, and continuously improve integration playbooks, frameworks, and best practices based on lessons learned from completed integrations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Map acquired entity chart of accounts to Banyan group standards and support alignment with group financial reporting

