&lt;li&gt;Review and maintain balance sheet reconciliations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee day-to-day accounting operations across assigned entities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with internal controls and support audit processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor cash flow and support forecasting activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with budgeting, forecasting, and variance analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare financial reports and ad-hoc financial analyses for business stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and implement process improvements through automation and technology solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the adoption of AI-driven tools for reporting and financial analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with operating company leadership and cross-functional teams to provide financial insights.&lt;

